    \approx 0.474\times10^{15}\ \text{Hz}
    \approx 4.74\times10^{14}\ \text{Hz}
\]

Thus the frequency, expressed in units of \(10^{14}\ \text{Hz}\), is

\[
\boxed{4.74}\;10^{14}\ \text{Hz}
\]

