\[
[\text{Ru}] = \frac{r_{H_2}}{k_{\rm Ru}}
= \frac{4.09\times10^{-3}}{92}=4.45\times10^{-5}\ \text{mol min}^{-1}
\]

The mass of Ru required:

\[
m_{\rm Ru}=4.45\times10^{-5}\,\text{mol}\times 101.07\ \text{g mol}^{-1}
=4.49\times10^{-3}\ \text{g}=4.49\ \text{mg}
\]

